thread.title_full: OptiContacts.com reviewed by pamela s preiss

author: pamela s preiss
title: pamela s preiss
text:
This was my first time ordering from OptiContacts. I read both good and bad reviews and decided to give them a try as they had good prices. I was not charged a shipping fee as I found a promo for free shipping. However, I was charged a processing fee which, in my opinion, was quite pricey. The order came in a very timely fashion. I am not sure if I will use them again as I heard once you re-order, the prices go up. We shall see.
So far, so good if it wasn't for the processing fee.
